Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:49.03,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,真朱 把ENTRE找出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:50.08,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:02:58.52,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:08.36,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然打倒了ASSET
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:10.36,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是得找出ENTRE啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.36,0:03:11.06,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:12.50,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个没用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.66,0:03:13.16,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:15.16,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:16.78,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,DIRECT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:19.11,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 随便你怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.27,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,我只把我损失的部分取回来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:24.39,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,CLOSING
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:25.37,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU HAVE GAIN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:26.33,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,做到了呢
